review:
I bought this device and it was delivered on the day, when I went outside the city, leaving it home. When I returned in two days, I connected it to charger, and started to set it up. Suddenly the screen started twinkling, the devise went hot and than it switched off; I couldn't turn it on, no matter how hard I tried;
I brought it to local official Samsung Service center and they told me some feature is crashed and nobody know why. Now I have to pay, additional USD 45 to fix it;
Is that normal? and only within two days!
Very disappointing!
